request.description:
### Retrieve Wishlist by ID

This endpoint retrieves a wishlist based on its unique ID.

#### Response

The response will be a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "books": {
            "type": "array"
        },
        "createdAt": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "updatedAt": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "id": {
            "type": "integer"
        }
    }
}

 ```
